\id 2CO - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project
\h 2 KOREN
\toc1 Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Koren Pon Kon Ena'
\toc2 2 Koren
\toc3 2 Koren
\mt2 Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ
\mt1 Koren Pon Kon
\mt2 Ena'
\imt1 Ekamanin
\ip \bk Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Koren Pon Kon Ena'\bk* e'menuka'pʉ sa'man pe kuru so'si Koren pon kon pokon pe tesi a'tai. So'si menpaai pe te'san tonpa ton uya pana' pe kuru Paarʉ ewa'nomato' tʉuya'nokon ku'sa' esi'pʉ, e'tane enpoika iya to' pokon pe ekonekapai kuru te'to' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨnekamapai iyesi eke pe tepori'mato' serɨ e'ku'sa' a'tai.
\ip Iye'sara'tɨ yau imenukasa' kareta yau Paarʉ usaurokʉ so'si Koren pon kon pokon pe te'to' pɨ', ɨ'rɨ wenai ɨsɨ pe ipan pe to' eikʉ'pʉ tʉuya to' uya tʉsapema mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tewa'noma pɨ' so'si tau ekama iya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pori' pe te'to' ekama iya ɨsɨ pe tesi'pʉ rʉ'pʉ otori'pɨ era'tɨn nɨsa' winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' pokon pe tekonekasa'. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan pe so'si ekama'po iya amʉre'mʉra to' uya itʉto' pe entu'manin nan Kʉri'san amʉ' Isutiya pon kon pika'tɨto' ike. Iu'matʉ yau'ne Paarʉ esi itekare ekamai' tenno'sa' wapu pe tu'kan kon pen ka'pon amʉ' Koren pon kon i'nairon kon itekare ekamai' enno'sa' kon pe iye'ku'sa' kon namai', Paarʉ pɨ' ennakanin tai'ma.
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1-11)
\io1 Paarʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ so'si Koren pon (1:12—7:16)
\io1 Tʉtʉsen Kʉri'san amʉ' Isutiya pokon iwano' pe (8:1—9:15)
\io1 Paarʉ e'to' itekare ekamai' tenno'sa' wapu pe (10:1—13:10)
\io1 Iu'matʉ (13:11-13)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paarʉ winɨpaino, Kʉrai Sises nennoko'pʉ itekare ekamai', Papa eseru poro, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Temu'ti, utonpa kon winɨpaino,\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 18:1\x*
\p Papa so'sii Koren pon pona kan, tanporo A'kaya poro te'san wakʉ ton Papa munkɨ amʉ' pokon pe:
\p 
\v 2 Wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉsewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' Papa, ukʉipʉnʉ kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Itepuru Sises Kʉrai winon nesii ɨyenau'nokon.
\s1 Papa, Tanporon A'kwarʉ Ne'nin Esa'
\p 
\v 3 Urɨ'nokon epuru Sises Kʉrai, e'to' itese' pɨ' Papa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Ikʉipʉnʉ, usentu'man nɨto' kʉipʉnʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa, tanporo a'kwarʉ ne'nin iwano' pe apurɨpɨ'to' nesii,
\v 4 uya'kwarʉ kon ne'nin tanporon nɨ mɨ awɨron nɨ ekamʉn uyepʉ uya uyewankama kon koro'tau, kamoro mɨrɨ waraino kon nɨ marɨ a'kwarʉ ne'to' pe, uya'kwarʉ kon uneporo'pʉ kon Papa winɨ ke.
\v 5 Kʉrai ekota'ma'pʉ ɨ'kwɨrɨtʉ uko'manto' kon ya' kasa rɨ, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ Kʉrai awɨrɨ uya'kwarʉ kon uye'sa' anʉkʉ.
\v 6 Mɨ awɨron nɨ ekamʉn uyepʉ uya ina ewankama yau, aya'kwarʉ kon ne'nin pe iyesi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨyepika'tɨto' kon pe nɨrɨ; ina a'kwarʉ ne'sa' pe iyesi yau, aya'kwarʉ kon uye'sa' pe iyesi, tʉuseta'kai' pʉra a'kʉre'tɨto' nepʉ iya ekota'man nɨto' ina ekota'ma'pʉ rɨ marɨ ipɨ' a'kʉre'tɨ kon pa.
\v 7 Ina e'ku'to' ɨpɨ'nokon esi pana' pe, apʉne pʉra ina uya i'tu ina ekota'ma'pʉ yau rɨ marɨ ɨuye'sa' kon tukai', mɨrɨ kasa rɨ ina a'kwarʉ uye'to' yau ɨuye'sa' kon.
\p 
\v 8 Auro'kasa' rʉ'pʉ pe pʉra rɨ ɨwesi kon i'se pʉra ina man, utonpa ton, sa'man ton yau ina ekota'ma'pʉ pɨ' Eisa Mʉre'pʉ awo'nan yau'ne. Eke kuru sa'man yau ina esi'pʉ, ina uya a'kʉre'tɨto' entai rɨ, tʉuko'mamʉ kon pen nɨ tukai' enari'ke' ina esi'pʉ.\x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1 Koren 15:32\x*
\v 9 I'nai rɨ tewan kon yau'ne iyeri'to' pe eno'masa' kasa ina usi'tu'pʉ, e'tane serɨ e'kupʉ'pʉ tʉpɨ'nokon nɨ ina uta'si namai' e'tane Papa pɨ' kuru, iyeri'sa' i'mʉ'sa'kanin.
\v 10 Ina pa'kasa' iya ɨsɨ kuru ma'tanʉ'nin apai, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina rɨ pa'ka iya. Kʉrɨ rɨ pɨ' te'ku'to' kon ku'sa' ina uya, miyarɨ rɨ ina pa'ka iya tukai',
\v 11 ɨwɨpʉremato' kon uya rɨ ina pika'tɨ koro'tau. Mɨrɨ a'tai rɨ si, tu'kan kon uya tenki tato' oton mɨrɨ ina iwano' pe\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Tu'ke rɨ imenukasa' ton uya, \fq ɨiwano' pe \ft ta.\f* eke pe rɨ Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' wenai, tu'kan kon ɨpʉremato' maimu ei'sa' wenai.
\s1 Paarʉ Eseru Usensima'pʉ
\p 
\v 12 Serɨ si ina utapurɨto': Ina ewan uya ekama teseru kon ku'sa' ina uya non yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ aya'kɨrɨ'nokon ɨpokon pe ina e'to' iyau kuru. Papa winon wakʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'napairon yau. Serɨ ku'sa' ina uya orʉ pu'ketʉ poro pʉra, e'tane Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' winɨ.
\v 13 Ina uya, ɨ'rɨ rɨ imenu ɨnenenʉ kon pen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨnto'ka'nʉkʉnʉ kon pen ke ɨmenuka kon pen. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ku'ai', tʉron nɨ a'tai tanporo ina to'ka'nʉkʉ auya'nokon mɨrɨ tukai',
\v 14 serɨ pe ipʉ'kʉ pe rɨ ina to'ka'nʉ'sa' auya'nokon e'tane, autapurɨ kon pa, ina utapurɨto' oton ɨpɨ'nokon na'ne' kasa Itepuru Sises weyu a'tai.
\p 
\v 15 Mɨrɨ pɨ' uyenu yau esi ke, wapiya aka'kʉranpato' kon pe uya ekoneka'pʉ asa' ite'kwa ɨyepika'tɨ kon pa.
\v 16 Aka'kʉranpato' kon pe uya ekoneka'pʉ kanan Ma'sitoniya pona utɨ pe rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpiya'nokon kanan tenna'poi' Ma'sitoniya apai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ utɨto' pe Isutiya pona uyennoko kon pa.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 19:21\x*
\v 17 Serɨ pɨ' ekonekasa' a'tai, usennakan pe rɨ pe' ikuu'pʉ uya? Mɨrɨ pe pʉra katɨ, ekonekato' kupʉ uya orʉ eseru poro, a'sa'tai rɨ, “Ewai', ewai',” mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, “Kane, kane,” tato' pe uya?
\p 
\v 18 E'tane i'napai rɨ tʉusauro'to' awɨrɨ Papa e'to' kasa, ɨyenakan kon ina ekareei esi “Ewai'” mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ “Kane” pe pen.
\v 19 Apʉne pʉra Papa Mumu, Sises Kʉrai, ɨ'koro'tau'nokon itekareei ekamasa' rʉ'pʉ urɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Sairas\f + \fr 1:19 \ft Kiri' \fq Sirʉpanas, Sairas \ft tato' tʉron nɨ pe.\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Temu'ti nekama'pʉ, esi'pʉ pen “Ewai'” pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ “Kane” pe nɨrɨ, e'tane iyau “Ewai'” pe rɨ iye'sa'.\x - \xo 1:19 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 18:5\x*
\v 20 Tu'ke rɨ tʉnku'ton pɨ' Papa usauro'sa', mɨrɨpan esi “Ewai'” pe'ne rɨ Kʉrai yau. Mɨrɨ wenai iporo “Amen” tasa' urɨ'nokon uya eke pe Papa kupʉ pe.
\v 21 Papa kuru rɨ kʉrɨ rɨ asa'rɨ rɨ marɨ pana' pe urɨ'nokon e'mʉ'sa'kato' emapu'tɨsa' iya na'ne' Kʉrai yau. Uyanʉnsa' iya 'nokon nɨ,
\v 22 tiwano' pe e'nɨ ekamanin a'sisa' iya upona'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Ta'kwarʉ emaikasa' iya uyewan kon ya', emaikasa' pe iye'to' pe, tiwano' pe e'nɨto' pe i'nai rɨ tʉuye'sen eporo ekamanin pe.
\p 
\v 23 Papa rɨ esi mɨrɨ uyekamanin pe, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon anma'tanʉ'pai pʉra esi wenai, Koren pona enna'po pʉra rɨ uye'sa'.
\v 24 Apurɨto' auya'nokon entai itesa' pe ina esi pen, e'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pokon pe ina e'tʉrawasoma ɨpori'ma kon pe, apʉne pʉra apurɨto' auya'nokon poro pana' pe ɨye'mʉ'sa'kasa' kon pɨ'.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Uyeseru koneka'pʉ uya, tʉron nɨ kanan e'ne' pe rɨ ɨku'to' kon pe aka'kʉranpa uya 'nokon namai'.
\v 2 Apʉne pʉra ɨpokoitanʉ'sa' uya 'nokon pe iyesi yau, ɨnʉ' e'ku'sa' upori'manin pe, e'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨken unpokoitanʉkʉ'san.
\v 3 Imenuka'pʉ uya na'ne' kasa imenuka'pʉ uya, uye'sa' a'tai isewankamasa' pe esi namai' upori'manin nan pe rɨ e'paino kon winɨ. Uyenu yau tanporo ɨwesi'pʉ kon tanporo pori' pe e'to' yau ɨwesi kon pa.
\v 4 Ɨmenuka'pʉ uya 'nokon, ipan pe usewankama mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ upokoitato' apai uyewan yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke pe rɨ uyenu ku'ma tenno'se, ɨpokoitanʉ'nin kon pe pen e'tane i'tu kon pa, uyewan yau ipan pe ɨi'nʉnka uya 'nokon.
\s1 Tʉmakooikenan Pɨ' Usentu'man
\p 
\v 5 Ɨnʉ' uya rɨ upokoitan emapu'tɨsa' yau, upokoitanʉ'sa' iya pʉra man tanporo ɨpokoitanʉ'sa' iya 'nokon na'ne' kasa, siya kuru pʉra rɨ—ipan pe kuru tʉusauro'se pʉra rɨ.
\v 6 Ikota'mato' ike pe tu'kan kon kuru rɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nʉtʉrʉ'pʉ nesii eke pe rɨ ipona.
\v 7 E'tane ru'ku nin, ipɨ' ɨsentu'matɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iya'kwarʉ ne'to' auya'nokon pe iyesi, ipan pe ipokoitato' uya eno'ma namai' itentai.
\v 8 Mɨrɨ pɨ' si iku'tɨ' ta uya serɨ ɨpɨ'nokon, i'nʉnkaka'tɨ' kanan.
\v 9 Ɨmenukasa' uya 'nokon na'ne' esi ɨi'tuto' kon pe' moronka auya'nokon tanporon awɨrɨ rɨ pe' ɨwesi kon ta uya wenai.
\v 10 Ɨnʉ' rɨ pɨ' ɨusentu'ma kon yau, urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ usentu'ma mɨrɨ ipɨ'. Ɨnʉ' pɨ' rɨ usentu'masa'—moro ipɨ' usentu'man nɨto' e'sa' yau—usentu'masa' mɨrɨ ipɨ' Kʉrai enu airɨ ɨpɨkɨrɨ'nokon,
\v 11 Se'tan\f + \fr 2:11 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* ena namai' uyentai'nokon, apʉne pʉra urɨ'nokon uya tʉnkupʉnʉ pɨ' iye'ku'to' i'tu pʉra iyesi pen.
\s1 Emenna' Ekonekan Nɨto' Tʉrawasomanin Nan
\p 
\v 12 Utɨsa' a'tai si Tʉrowas pona Kʉrai ekareei ekamase'na, eporo'pʉ uya Itepuru uya mʉra'ta a'kokasa' esi'pʉ uiwano' pe,\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 20:1\x*
\v 13 usewankaman pɨ' rɨ esi'pʉ, apʉne pʉra utonpa Tai'tas eposa' uya pʉra iyesi pɨ' mɨrɨ yau. Mɨrɨ pɨ' si, “Ɨisirɨ, utɨyai',” ta'pʉ uya mɨrɨ to' pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ utɨ'pʉ Ma'sitoniya pona.
\p 
\v 14 E'tane tenki ta uya Papa pɨ', uyanin kon ye' inke rɨ Sises Kʉrai yau itentai ina enasa' utɨto' yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ'nokon poro iye'ta'nʉkʉ mɨ awɨrɨ rɨ i'tuto' kɨtun.
\v 15 Apʉne pʉra Papa pona ina esi Kʉrai na'po'nanʉkʉ'san pe tʉukɨ'nʉnsan pe kamoro iyepika'tɨsa' kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan pɨ' na'ne' nan koro'tawon kon.
\v 16 Tʉron kon pona ikɨ pe e'nɨ'nokon, iyeri'sa' ukɨtasa' kɨtun ke; tʉron kon pona uko'man nɨto' a'po'nanʉʉi pe e'nɨ'nokon. Ɨnʉ' ken si nai serɨ tʉrawaso kaisa rɨ?
\v 17 Tu'ke te'sen kasa pʉra rɨ, Papa maimu kʉrʉpo'poma pɨ' ina esi pen. Mɨrɨ kasa pen nin, Kʉrai yau ina usaurokʉ Papa rau wakʉ pe Papa nennoko'san kon ka'pon amʉ' pe.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Utapurɨn pɨ' kanan pe' ina epiya'tɨ serɨ? Mɨrɨ pe pʉra katɨ tʉron kon ka'pon amʉ' kasa, imenukasa' kareta i'se ina esi ina ekamanin ɨpɨ'nokon mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨpiyapai'nokon?
\v 2 Ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ kamoro imenukasa' ton kareta amʉ', imenukasa' ton ina ewan pɨ', ti'tusan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon nɨ nenenʉ ton imenu.
\v 3 Enpoika auya'nokon imenukasa' kareta Kʉrai winon pe ɨwesi kon, ina e'tʉrawasomasa' otori'san, imenukasa' pen paru ke pen e'tane Papa tʉuko'mansen A'kwarʉ ke, tɨ' konekasa' iyapon pɨ' pen e'tane ka'pon amʉ' ewan ton esi iyapon pe.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt E'sotas 24:12; Iseremaya 31:33; Isi'kiyerʉ 11:19; 36:26\x*
\p 
\v 4 Serɨ waraino en yau e'nɨto' esi ina iwano' pe Kʉrai poro Papa rau.
\v 5 Tiwano' kon pe serɨ kupʉ ina uya ta pen, e'tane Papa winɨ iku'to' ina uya ike uyepʉ.
\p 
\v 6 Ina ku'sa' iya apiyo' pe emenna' pe ekonekan nɨto' tʉrawasomanin nan pe, imenukasa' kareta pen e'tane Iya'kwarʉ; apʉne pʉra imenukasa' kareta uya iwɨnɨ, e'tane Iya'kwarʉ uya uko'man nɨto' tʉrʉ.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Iseremaya 31:31\x*
\s1 Emenna' Ekonekan Nɨto' A'kwarii
\p 
\v 7 Penaro' iteseru, uma'tan nɨ ne'nin, e'menukasa' tɨ' pɨ' uye'sa' pe iyesi yau Esuwerʉ amʉ' uya, inke tenu kon tʉtʉse Mosi' enpɨtʉ namai' apʉne pʉra a'kwa pe iyesi pɨ' iyenpuru'na tane rɨ.\x - \xo 3:7 \xt E'sotas 34:29\x*
\v 8 Mɨrɨ entai pe' a'kwa pe Iya'kwarʉ eseru esi pen mɨ?
\v 9 Penaro' iteseru ka'pon nɨ uma'ta ku'nin uye'sa' yau a'kwa pe, mɨrɨ entai a'kwa pe ipokena' pe e'nɨto' ne'nin esi!
\v 10 A'kwa pe iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ esi eke pe iku'to' ipɨkɨrɨ pʉra, apʉne pʉra eke kuru emenna' iteseru a'kwa uye'sa' pɨ'.
\v 11 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tenpuru'nasen uye'sa' pe iyesi yau a'kwa pe, mɨrɨ entai rɨ nin tʉuko'mansen a'kwa esi mɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', mɨrɨ warai e'ku'nɨto' esi pɨ', ipan pe enari'mʉra e'nɨ.
\v 13 Mosi' kasa e'nɨ pen, temʉ' nɨpontɨnin iwon ke Esuwerʉ amʉ' uya enkena' pe iye'sa' enpuru'na ene namai'.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt E'sotas 34:33\x*
\v 14 E'tane to' usenuminkato' ena'pʉ i'tunin ye' pe pʉra rɨ, apʉne pʉra serɨ wʉi pʉ'kʉ pona mɨrɨ rɨ iwon esi moro rɨ, penaro' ekonekan nɨsa' rʉ'pʉ usekama a'tai. Itamasa' pʉra rɨ iyesi, apʉne pʉra Kʉrai yau rɨken iyemo'kato' esi.
\v 15 Serɨ wʉi pʉ'kʉ pona rɨ Papa nʉnonka'pʉ main Mosi' poro usekama a'tai, iwon uya rɨ to' ewan ton nɨpontɨ.
\v 16 E'tane ɨnʉ' rɨ era'tɨ a'tai Itepuru winɨkʉi', iwon nin si emo'ka.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt E'sotas 34:34\x*
\v 17 Mɨrɨ si Itepuru esi Iya'kwarʉ pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Itepuru A'kwarʉ na'ne' airɨ imo'kasa' pe e'nɨ.
\v 18 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo urɨ'nokon, itemʉ' iwonkasa' ton uya Itepuru a'kwarii rɨ a'kwarʉ'pʉ enpoika, usensimasa' ikasa miyarɨ rɨ a'kwa pe enan nɨto' ke, tʉuye'sen Itepuru winɨ, Iya'kwarʉ pe si na'ne'.
\c 4
\s1 Mamin Ɨinɨ Pun Ka'sa' Wai Yawon
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Papa ɨsentu'kena' pe tesi ke ina repasa' iya tʉrawaso ke ina uya iku'to' pe, mɨrɨ pɨ' si ina uya inonka pʉra iyesi.
\v 2 Ina uya mɨ airɨ tanporo ama'aino mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri piyɨ'nʉ'nin nonkasa'; kasi awɨrɨ ina esi pen. Mɨrɨ pe pʉra Papa Maimu kupʉ ina uya pen kasi ye' pe, mɨrɨ pe pʉra nin, i'nairon ekama pɨ' ina e'tʉsa' tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' ewan ya' Papa enu yau.
\v 3 Ɨ'rɨ pe pʉra ina ekareei e'nɨpontɨ pe iyesi yau, iye'nɨpontɨ kamoro tʉuma'tasan pona.
\v 4 Papa pe te'ku'sen, serɨ a'taino kon e'to' itese' pɨ' uya apurɨnin nan pen usenuminkato' enku'nanʉ'sa', to' uya itekare weyu ene namai' Kʉrai ku'to' eke pe ipɨ', Papa pe te'sen.
\v 5 Apʉne pʉra tekareei kon ekama ina uya pen, e'tane Sises Kʉrai Itepuru pe, ina nin si ɨpoitorʉ kon pe Sises uriya'.
\v 6 Apʉne pʉra Papa, “Tɨwɨ a'kwa ne'wei'tɨi ewarupɨ apai,”\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Iseneses 1:3\f* tawon nʉ'pʉ uya tʉweyu e'wei'tɨto' pe iku'sa' uyewan kon yau uwei'tɨnin kon pe eke pe Papa ku'to' i'tunin pe e'nɨto' kon pe Kʉrai emʉ' yau.
\p 
\v 7 E'tane serɨ mamin esa' pe ina esi ɨinɨ pun ka'sa' wai yau enpoikanin pe serɨ tanporon nɨ entaino meruntɨ esi Papa winon pe, ina winon pe pʉra.
\v 8 Ina pona ekamʉn nʉye'an sen winɨ'ne rɨ, e'tane ina ma'tanʉ'sa' iya pʉra rɨ iyesi; enpikaimapɨ'sa' pe, e'tane mɨrɨ pɨ' ina enari'nʉnsa' pʉra rɨ;
\v 9 tʉkota'masen pe rɨ, e'tane inonkasa' pe pʉra rɨ; iwɨsa' uta'mo'kasa' pe, e'tane ima'tanʉ'sa' pe pʉra rɨ.
\v 10 Tɨwɨrɨ rɨ ina pun esi Sises uma'ta'pʉ ekamanin ye' pe rɨ, iko'manto' usenpoikato' pe rɨ marɨ ina uko'manto' yau.
\v 11 Apʉne pʉra ina nurɨnan kon esi tʉtʉsan pe tɨwɨrɨ rɨ uma'tan nɨto' ya' Sises Kʉrai uriya', iko'manto' usenpoikato' pe tʉuma'tasen ina pun yau.
\v 12 Mɨrɨ kasa si, uma'tan nɨto' e'tʉrawasoma ina yau, e'tane uko'man nɨto' e'tʉrawasoma ayau'nokon.
\p 
\v 13 Iye'menukasa': “Apurɨsa' uya; mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', usauro'sa',”\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Eren 116:10 (LXX)\f* tukai'. Mɨrɨ rɨ apurɨto' iya'kwarʉ pe ina uya rɨ marɨ apurɨ, mɨrɨ pɨ' ina usaurokʉ,
\v 14 apʉne pʉra ina uya i'tu kʉrɨ rɨ rɨ Itepuru i'mʉ'sa'kanin nʉ'pʉ iyerikʉ'pʉ yapai uya rɨ marɨ ina i'mʉ'sa'ka Sises pokon pe, mɨrɨpan uya ina tʉrʉ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon pokon pe tʉpiya'.
\v 15 Tanporo serɨ esi ɨiwano' kon pe rɨ, wakʉ nonkasa' uya miyarɨ rɨ ka'pon amʉ' eporo uya, uya tenki tato' ku'to' pe eke pe itentai, eke pe Papa ku'to' iwano' pe.
\p 
\v 16 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ina uya inonka pen. Kɨpo'po ina a'mota tane, e'tane ti'nau'nokon ina ena emenna' pe wʉi kaisarɨ rɨ.
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra usewankaman nɨto' esi mara rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ aka'nero' pe rɨ, mɨrɨpan uya konekan eke pe e'nɨto', aka'nero' pen eponin pe eke pe rɨ mɨrɨ ton entai.
\v 18 Mɨrɨ wenai, tenu kon tʉsa' ina uya tensen pɨ' pen, e'tane tensen pen pɨ'. Apʉne pʉra tensen esi aka'nero' pe rɨ, e'tane tensen pen esi inkero' pe rɨ.
\c 5
\s1 Epʉn Pon Uiwʉ' Kon
\p 
\v 1 Serɨ si i'tu'nokon, serɨ non po e'nɨ'nokon iwʉ', upun kon, ta'porin kasa te'sen uma'tasa' pe iyesi yau, uiwʉ' kon esi mɨrɨ Papa winon, inkero' nin uiwʉ' kon Epʉn pon, ka'pon emiyatʉ ke amɨsa' pen.
\v 2 Mɨrɨ koro'tau rɨ, a'nʉn nɨ pɨ' e'nɨ, Epʉn pon uiwʉ' kon ke upontɨkapʉ kon i'se,
\v 3 epontɨn nɨsa' a'tai ipon pʉra eporon pen nɨ.
\v 4 Serɨ si ta'porin tau e'nɨ koro'tau, a'nʉn nɨ, iwari'sa'tɨsa' kon pe e'nɨ, apʉne pʉra uponka kon i'se pʉra e'nɨ wenai e'tane upontɨ kon i'se e'nɨ Epʉn pon uiwʉ' kon ke, tʉuma'tasen pe te'sen usenko'masa' e'to' pe uko'man nɨto' ike ke.
\v 5 Papa si kʉrɨ rɨ uka'nin nʉ'pʉ kon serɨto' pe, mɨrɨpan uya urepasa' kon Ita'kwarʉ ke emaikasa' pe, tʉuye'ton e'ma takan pe.
\p 
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', uyenu kon yawon kon nɨ urɨ'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tu'nokon upun kon yau e'nɨ'nokon a'tai, Itepuru piyau pʉra rɨ e'nɨ'nokon.
\v 7 Uko'man nɨ'nokon serɨ apurɨto' winɨ, ene winɨ pen.
\v 8 Uyenu kon awon kon urɨ'nokon, ta uya, mɨrɨpan e'nɨ'nokon upun kon yau e'pai pʉra Itepuru piyau rɨken e'pai.
\v 9 Uyeseru kon nin si esi ɨnpori'mapai te'sen pe, upun kon yau e'nɨ yau rɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra ipiyapai rɨ e'nɨ yau.
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra usenpoikan nɨto' oton kon Kʉrai uya eseru aimenkato' apon rakʉi', ukaisarɨ'nokon uneporonʉ kon epose'na unkupʉ'pʉ kon pɨkɨrɨ upun kon yau e'nɨ'nokon koro'tau, wakʉ rɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨri rɨ.\x - \xo 5:10 \xt Ron 14:10\x*
\s1 Ipokon Pe Ekonekan Tʉrawasooi
\p 
\v 11 Mɨrɨ si'kɨrɨ Itepuru pɨ' enari'nʉn nɨ i'tu'nokon ke, ka'pon amʉ' nin si anra'tɨpai e'nɨ. E'nɨ na'ne'nokon esi tense rɨ Papa pona, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ku'ai' tense rɨ nɨrɨ iyesi e'pai man ɨyewan kon yau.
\v 12 Ɨyena'nokon kanan e'tʉpai ina esi pen, e'tane ina pɨ' tʉutapurɨsen pe ɨwesi kon pa, kamoro tensen pɨ' ewan yawon pen nɨ pɨ' tʉutapurɨsan ei'nin nan pe ɨwesi kon pa.
\v 13 I'pai itano'masa' pe ina esi yau, Papa iwano' pe iyesi mɨrɨ; wakʉ pe ina i'pai esi yau, ɨiwano' kon pe iyesi mɨrɨ.
\v 14 Apʉne pʉra Kʉrai usi'nʉnkato' uya ina a'kwarʉka pe rɨ iyesi, apʉne pʉra ina uya apurɨ tikin nan nɨ erikʉ'pʉ tanporon kon iwano' pe, mɨrɨ pɨ' si tanporon kon nɨ erikʉ'pʉ.
\v 15 Tanporon kon iwano' pe iyerikʉ'pʉ kamoro si nʉko'manyai'ne' nan uko'mamʉ namai' tiwano' kon pe, e'tane kʉrɨ tiwano' kon pe iyeri'sa' rʉ'pʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iye'mʉ'sa'kaka'sa' rʉ'pʉ kanan iwano' pe.
\p 
\v 16 Serɨ awonsi'kɨ nin si, ka'pon pɨ' ina usenuminkato' pʉra iyesi mɨrɨ non pon pe e'nɨ eseru yau. Serɨ kasa rɨ Kʉrai pɨ' ina usenuminka'pʉ rɨ e'tane pena, serɨ pe mɨrɨ kupʉ ina uya pen.
\v 17 Ɨnʉ' rɨ esi yau Kʉrai iwano' pe, emenna' pe ika'sa' pe iyesi mɨrɨ; penaro' utɨ'pʉ, emenna' uye'sa'!
\v 18 Tanporo serɨ ton esi Papa winon pe, tʉwinɨkʉi' ukonekanin nʉ'pʉ kon Kʉrai poro mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉpokon pe tʉron kon konekato' pe utʉrawasooi kon ke urepasa' iya 'nokon;
\v 19 Papa esi'pʉ tʉpokon pe orʉ ekoneka i'se Kʉrai yau, ka'pon amʉ' pɨ' tʉmakooi ke to' esi tukai' pʉra. Mɨrɨpan uya tʉpokon pe ekonekan ekareei nonkasa' ina ena'.
\v 20 Ina nin si esi serɨ Kʉrai nennoko'san pe tʉpe rɨ, Papa uya ɨyekama'posa' kon kuru ina poro. Ina uya kuru ɨyekama'po kon ipan pe Kʉrai iwano' pe: Papa pokon pe ekonekaka'tɨ'.
\v 21 Papa uya tʉmakooikenan pen nɨ kuu'pʉ makoi pe\f + \fr 5:21 \fq makoi pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq makoi e'mato' ike pe\f* uiwano' kon pe, Papa e'to' ipokena' pe eponin nan pe ekonekan nɨto' kon pe ipokon pe.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Papa pokon pe a'samʉtʉ yau te'tʉrawasomasan pe ina esi pɨ' ina uya kuru ɨyekama'po kon, wakʉ nonkasa' Papa uya na'ne' anʉnsa' auya'nokon esi namai' notʉn pe.
\v 2 Apʉne pʉra ta iya,
\q1 “Wakʉ pe e'to' weyu a'tai ɨyeta'pʉ uya,
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ epika'tɨn weyu a'tai ɨpika'tɨ'pʉ uya,”\f + \fr 6:2 \ft Aisaya 49:8\f*
\m ta iya. Apana'tɨ uya 'nokon, serɨ kuru si serɨ wakʉ pe Papa e'to' weyu, serɨ pe kuru si man epika'tɨn weyu pe.
\s1 Sa'man Yau Paarʉ E'to'
\p 
\v 3 Ɨnʉ' e'ma ta' rɨ uta'mo'kan nɨto' rɨ tʉrʉ ina uya pʉra man, ina tʉrawasooi sapema namai'.
\v 4 E'tane nin, tanporon yau rɨ Papa poitorʉ ton pe ina usenpoika: sa'man nɨ; ɨsɨ rɨ moronka pɨ', ewankamanin nɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ aimerunpanin nɨ moronka ina uya;
\v 5 ari'po'pɨ'nɨto', pariki'si ta' a'sin nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ anpisin usewa'noma koro'tau rɨ; sa'man pe e'tʉrawasoman pɨ', e'nʉnpai e'nɨ tane e'nʉn nɨ pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iwan pe.\x - \xo 6:5 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:23\x*
\v 6 Se ton moronka ina uya, wakʉ pe kuru ina e'to' yau, ito'ka'nʉkʉ yau, tʉuseta'kai' pʉra e'nɨto' yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mannʉ' pe e'nɨto' yau; Wakʉ A'kwarʉ yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nai rɨ usi'nʉnkan nɨto' yau;
\v 7 i'nairon main yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa meruntɨrʉ yau; ipoken ina e'to' esi ina epaai pe tanporon yau rɨ, siyauya'ne rɨ;
\v 8 eke pe ina ku'to' winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina nama pʉra ina e'to' winɨ, ina apurɨpɨ'to' winɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina pona eno'ma winɨ; i'nairon pe, e'tane kasi ye' tato' ipɨ' ton pe.
\v 9 Se ton moronka ina uya, ti'tusan ye', e'tane ti'tusan ye' pen kasa; eri'nɨ pɨ', mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane ina rɨ uko'mamʉ; ari'po'pɨ'sa' pe, e'tane iyeri'sa' pe pʉra;
\v 10 tewankono'mai', e'tane tɨwɨrɨ rɨ pori' pe; entu'ma', e'tane tu'kan kon nɨ kupʉ pɨ' imaminke' pe; ɨ'rɨ esa' pe pʉra rɨ, e'tane tanporon nɨ esa' pe.
\p 
\v 11 Tʉwapu'tɨi' pʉra rɨ ina uya ayauro'kasa' kon man, Koren pon kon, ina uya rɨ nɨrɨ tewan kon a'kokasa' eke pe ɨyena'nokon.
\v 12 Ina uya rɨ ɨi'nʉnkato' tʉuya'nokon enkurunpa pen ɨpiyapai'nokon, e'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uya nin ina i'nʉnkato' auya'nokon enkurunpa mɨrɨ ina piyapai.
\v 13 Umunkɨ amʉ' pe kuru, ayauro'ka uya 'nokon serɨ, mɨrɨ entakanoma pe, ɨyewan kon a'kokatɨ' eke pe rɨ marɨ.
\s1 Apurɨnin Nan Pen Pokon Pe Ke'pʉmʉkantʉu
\p 
\v 14 Apurɨnin nan pen pokon pe a'samʉtʉ ya' ke'pʉmʉkantʉu. Ɨ'rɨ kasa ipoken e'nɨto' nesii'no ɨsi'kaisa rɨ ɨri pe e'nɨto' pokon pe? Mɨrɨ pe pʉra, nai kasa a'kwa esi ɨsi'kaisa rɨ ewarupɨ pokon pe?
\v 15 Ɨ'rɨ kasa pori' pe Kʉrai nesii'no Periyarʉ\f + \fr 6:15 \fq Periyarʉ, \ft Kiri' maimu yau ese' Sepan nɨ ta e'kwa, Makoi ese' tonpa.\f* pokon pe? Ɨ'rɨ kasa apurɨnin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨnin pen nesii'no ɨsi'kaisa rɨ?
\v 16 Ɨ'rɨ kasa ɨseseru yau Papa ena' use'man nɨto', ɨpʉreman nɨto' iwʉ' nesii'no papa tato' pe ika'sa' pokon pe? Apʉne pʉra urɨ'nokon esi nurɨnan Papa ena' use'man nɨto', ɨpʉreman nɨto' iwʉ' pe, Papa uya tasa' na'ne' kasa rɨ, “To' piyau uko'mamʉ mɨrɨ, to' koro'tau rɨ usarɨ, to' e'to' itese' pɨ' pe rɨ esi, mɨrɨpan kon esi umunkɨ pe rɨ.”\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Ripaiti'kas 26:12; Iseremaya 32:38; Isi'kiyerʉ 37:27; 1 Koren 3:16; 6:19.\f*
\q1 
\v 17 “Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', to' koro'tapai epa'katɨ',
\q2 tʉpona rɨ enatɨ',
\qr ta Itepuru uya.
\q1 Ɨri rɨ kʉsa'pɨ'pɨ'tʉu,
\q2 mɨrɨ a'tai ayanʉmʉ uya 'nokon.”\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Aisaya 52:11; Isi'kiyerʉ 20:34, 41\f*
\q1 
\v 18 “Ɨkʉipʉnʉ kon pe e'to' pe,
\q2 mɨrɨ a'tai umunkɨ amʉ' pe, uyensi ton pe ɨwe'to' kon pe,
\qr ta Itepuru meruntɨ pe kuru te'sen uya,”\f + \fr 6:18 \ft 2 Sanwerʉ 7:8, 14; 1 Kʉrono'kʉrʉs 17:13; Aisaya 43:6; Iseremaya 31:9.\f*
\m tasa'.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Serɨ ton si iku'to' pe usauro'nɨsa' eposa'nokon pɨ', utonpa ton amʉ' rʉ'kwɨ, ekorʉkanpai'nokon tanporon ɨri ton apai upun kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uya'kwarʉ kon ma'tanʉ'sa' iya na'ne', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ miyarɨ'nokon wakʉ pe e'nɨto' ya' Papa tʉnamai' e'nɨto' winɨ.
\s1 Paarʉ E'to' Pori' Pe
\p 
\v 2 Ɨyewan kon yau ina pata oton ɨnkonekatɨ'. Ɨnʉ' rɨ ku'sa' ina uya pʉra man ipoken pʉra, ɨnʉ' rɨ ma'tanʉ'sa' ina uya pʉra man, ɨnʉ' pɨ' rɨ ina usennakasa' pʉra man.
\v 3 Ɨyeno'ma kon pe serɨ ta uya pen; wapiya takaa'pʉ uya apata kon nɨ esi ina ewan yau, ɨiwano' kon pe rɨ ina uko'mamʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina rɨ uma'ta ɨpokon pe.
\v 4 Uyenu yau kuru rɨ ɨwesi kon; mɨ pe kuru ukupʉ auya'nokon. Eke pe kuru upori'ma auya'nokon; tanporon nɨ ina ewankamanin yau pori' pe e'to' rɨ anʉkʉ.
\p 
\v 5 Apʉne pʉra ina utɨsa' a'tai Ma'sitoniya pona, ina pun umoronka'to' a'tai pʉra rɨ iyesi'pʉ, ina ewankamanin esi'pʉ sen winɨ'ne rɨ—kɨpo'po ina ewa'noma mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enari'nʉn nɨ ina yau.\x - \xo 7:5 \xt 2 Koren 2:13\x*
\v 6 E'tane Papa iseno'masa' rɨ a'kwarʉ wannɨ ne'nin uya ina a'kwarʉ ne'sa' Tai'tas tenno'se,
\v 7 iyepʉ uya rɨken pen e'tane iya'kwarʉ ne'sa' auya'nokon ke rɨ nɨrɨ. Ina pɨ' ekama'pʉ iya, upɨ' ɨusentu'mato' kon, ipan pe ɨupokoita kon, upika'tɨ pɨ' a'ne' pe ɨwe'to' kon, mɨrɨ uya miyarɨ rɨ eke pe pori' pe e'to' pe uku'to' pe.
\p 
\v 8 Ɨ'rɨ pe pʉra pokoi pe ukaretaai unennoko'pʉ uya ɨku'sa' kon e'tane, aiko ta uya pen nɨ. Aiko ta'pʉ uya rɨ e'tane—ene uya ukaretaai uya e'ne' pe ɨku'sa' kon, e'tane aka'ne' pe rɨ—
\v 9 e'tane nin si serɨ si pori' pe esi, pokoi pe ɨku'sa' kon pɨ' pen e'tane ɨpokooi kon uya ɨyera'tɨ kon ku'sa' pɨ' amakooi kon apai. Ɨusewankama'pʉ kon Papa iwano' pe rɨ mɨrɨ pɨ' ina winɨ rɨ e'ne' pe ɨyena'pʉ kon pen nɨ.
\v 10 Papa uya tasa' kasa upokoitan nɨsa' uya era'tɨn kupʉ, epika'tɨn nɨto' winɨkʉi' arɨn nɨ iya. Mɨrɨ pɨ' usewankaman pen, e'tane serɨ non pon kon pe upokoitan nɨto' uya uma'tan nɨto' nepʉ.
\v 11 Entɨ' serɨ Papa uya tasa' kasa ipan pe pokoi pe e'nɨto' uya ɨku'sa' kon: temetarunsan pe pʉra, inke pʉra ipoken ku'nin pe tʉusenpoikasen pe, tʉusakorotasan pe ekamʉra ɨku'sa' kon pɨ', tetʉipɨ'san pe, tʉusi'nʉnkasan pe, tʉusewankamasan pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨye'kamasa' kon ɨsi'kaisa rɨ iye'kupʉ ene kon pa. Tanporon yau rɨ wakʉ pe ɨwesi kon tukai' ɨusi'tu kon serɨ ton yau.
\v 12 Mɨrɨ pɨ' si ɨmenukasa' uya 'nokon nɨ e'tane ipokena' pen ku'nin nʉ'pʉ pɨ' pen nɨ, e'ne' pe iku'sa' kon pɨ' rɨ nɨrɨ pen, e'tane Papa rau ɨiwano' kon pe ɨusene kon pa, wakʉ pe kuru ina pɨ' iye'tʉsa' kon.
\v 13 Serɨ ton uya rɨ ina pori'ma.
\p Ina epori'mapɨ'to' pirikʉ pe rɨ, ina esi'pʉ pori' pe, Tai'tas esi pori' pe tense, apʉne pʉra ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uya ipika'tɨsa' wakʉ pe itewan ku'sa' ke.
\v 14 Ipɨ' ɨpɨ'nokon utapurɨto' kuu'pʉ uya, mɨrɨpan upiyɨ'nʉ'sa' auya'nokon pʉra iyesi. E'tane tanporon nɨ ekamasa' na'ne' ɨpɨ'nokon esi'pʉ i'nairɨ ikasa rɨ, mɨrɨpan si ɨpɨ'nokon utapurɨn nɨsa' Tai'tas pɨ' usi'tusa' i'nairɨ rɨ nɨrɨ.
\v 15 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨi'nʉnkato' iya 'nokon esi miyarɨ rɨ eke pe, tenu yau ɨkupʉ tʉuya'nokon a'tai main awɨrɨ ɨwesi'pʉ kon, Tai'tas ereutanʉkʉ'pʉ auya'nokon, eke pe inamato' auya'nokon ke, ɨnku'pai ɨwesi kon pɨ'.
\v 16 Epori'mayai' mararon pe pʉra uyenu yau ɨkupʉ uya 'nokon pe iyesi pɨ'.
\c 8
\s1 Amʉre'mʉra E'nɨto' Pe Pori'man
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ pe si utonpa ton i'tu auya'nokon i'se ina esi wakʉ nonkasa' Papa uya na'ne' Ma'sitoniya pon so'si ton ena' intʉrʉ'pʉ pɨ'.
\v 2 Ɨsɨ ton kuru i'tupɨ'nɨto' apai, eke rɨ to' epori'mato' anʉ'sa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan nɨ itimamin pʉra to' e'to' ena'pʉ amʉre'mʉra e'nɨto' yau imaminkena' pe.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra ekama uya to' uya itʉrʉ'pʉ eke pe kuru rɨ itʉto' tʉuya'nokon kaisa rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itʉto' tʉuya'nokon entai kuru rɨ nɨrɨ. Tanporo kuru tiwano' kon pe,
\v 4 inke pʉra ina pɨ' to' uta'kwarʉka'pʉ wakʉ ton pika'tɨkapʉ pɨ' serɨ e'repan nɨto' yau.\x - \xo 8:4 \xt Ron 15:26\x*
\v 5 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina e'to' itenupɨkɨrɨ kasa pʉra to' uya ikupʉ'pʉ pen, e'tane wapiya Itepuru ena' to' e'tʉrʉ'pʉ tiwano' kon pe mɨrɨ tʉpo ina ena', Papa eseru awɨrɨ tesi kon ekamanin pe.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pɨ' Tai'tas enutɨ'pʉ ina uya, wapiya isara'tɨsa' iya pɨ' rɨ, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon iwano' pe nɨrɨ iu'ma'to' ya' ine'to' pe iya, serɨ wakʉ nonkasa' nʉkupʉnʉ.
\v 7 E'tane tanporon nɨ kupʉ auya'nokon pɨ' ɨnkupʉnʉ kon yau wakʉ pe—apurɨto' auya'nokon yau, ausauro'to' kon yau, i'tuto' auya'nokon yau, ɨnku'pai e'nɨto' enuka'nʉ'sa' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina i'nʉnka auya'nokon yau\f + \fr 8:7 \ft Tʉron nɨ imenukasa' uya, \fq ɨi'nʉnka uya 'nokon yau, \ft tawon esi.\f*—entɨ' kanan serɨ e'repan nɨto' kupʉ auya'nokon wakʉ nonkasa' yau.
\p 
\v 8 Ayapiyo'ma uya 'nokon pen nɨ e'tane i'nairon ɨusi'nʉnkato' kon i'tupɨtʉ i'se esi, tʉron kon e'to' ɨnku'pai kaisa rɨ ti'tui'.
\v 9 Apʉne pʉra i'tu auya'nokon, uyepuru kon Sises Kʉrai uya wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ imaminkena' pe rɨ esii'ma, mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane ɨwenai'nokon entu'ma' iyena'pʉ, entu'ma' iyenasa' winɨ imaminkena' pe ɨyena kon pa.
\v 10 Nʉtɨtaine' wʉipiya yau ɨmɨrɨ'nokon esi'pʉ iwapiya itʉnin pe rɨken pen e'tane ɨnku'pai nɨrɨ ɨwesi'pʉ kon. Serɨ si apanamato' uya 'nokon wakʉ pe kuru te'sen ɨiwano' kon pe serɨ yau.
\v 11 Serɨ si tʉrawaso i'ma'katɨ', mɨrɨ si ɨnku'pai ɨwe'to' kon uya iu'ma'to' uya enpoikato' pe ɨnku'pai ɨwe'to' kon awɨrɨ.
\v 12 Apʉne pʉra mɨrɨ yau ɨnku'pai ɨwe'to' kon esi yau, ɨye'repato' kon esi tapurɨsen pe rɨ ɨpiyau'nokon na'ne' awɨrɨ, ɨpiyau'nokon pʉra na'ne' awɨrɨ pen.
\p 
\v 13 Ina e'to' i'se esi pen tʉron kon pika'tɨi'ma sa'man pe ɨkupʉ kon pɨ', e'tane ɨsi'kaisa rɨ e'nɨto' e'to' pe.
\v 14 Serɨ pe kuru eke pe ɨpiyau'nokon na'ne' uya ipan pe i'se to' e'to' ke to' pika'tɨ, mɨrɨ enta' eke pe to' piyau te'sen uya ipan pe i'se ɨwe'to' kon ke ɨpika'tɨ kon. Mɨrɨ a'tai nin si ɨsi'kaisa rɨ ɨwe'to' oton kon mɨrɨ,
\v 15 iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa: “Kʉrɨ eke pe amʉranʉ'nin nʉ'pʉ piyau eke pe kuru pʉra iyesi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ aiko pe amʉranʉ'nin nʉ'pʉ piyau aiko pe iyesi pen,”\f + \fr 8:15 \ft E'sotas 16:18\f* tawon.
\s1 Tai'tas Ennoko'pʉ Koren Pona
\p 
\v 16 Papa pɨ' tenki ta uya usewankamato' rɨ marɨ ɨpɨ'nokon emaikanin nʉ'pʉ pɨ' Tai'tas ewan ya'.
\v 17 Ina nekama'ponʉ pɨ' rɨken Tai'tas epori'ma'pʉ pen e'tane ɨpiya'nokon ɨtɨpai te'to' kuru pokon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tiwano' pe rɨ.
\v 18 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉtonpa kon nɨrɨ ennoko pɨ' ina man iya'kɨrɨ tanporo so'si amʉ' napurɨpɨtʉnʉ wakʉ itekare pɨ' iye'tʉrawasoma pɨ'.
\v 19 Mɨrɨ entai kuru, so'si amʉ' uya anʉnsa' ina tonpa pe itɨto' pe tʉtʉsen arɨ ina uya koro'tau ina nʉtʉrʉnʉ Itepuru nama tʉuya'nokon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan pe epika'tɨpai ina e'to' enpoikanin pe.
\p 
\v 20 E'sapeman nɨto' pʉra iye'to' pe ikupʉ i'se ina esi, eke tʉtʉsen pe tʉron kon nʉtʉrʉ'pʉ tʉrawasoma eseru.
\v 21 Ipoken te'sen kupʉ pɨ' e'pai ina esi, Itepuru enu yau rɨken pen, e'tane ka'pon amʉ' enu yau rɨ nɨrɨ.\x - \xo 8:21 \xt Ipu'ketʉ 3:4 (LXX)\x*
\p 
\v 22 Mɨrɨ pona, to' a'kɨrɨ tʉtonpa kon ennoko pɨ' ina man; tu'kan winɨ rɨ ɨnku'paino pe isenpoikasa', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨrɨ entai rɨ apʉne pʉra eke pe kuru itenu yau ɨwesi kon.
\v 23 Tai'tas nin si esi mɨrɨ uisakon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'tʉrawasoma tonpa pe ɨ'koro'tau'nokon; tʉron kon ina tonpa ton nʉtɨyai'ne' nan nin si esi mɨrɨ so'si amʉ' maimu ekamanin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai nama pe.
\v 24 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ipan pe to' i'nʉnkatɨ' ɨpɨ'nokon ina utapurɨto' enpoika pe tanporo so'si ton uya ento' pe.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Ɨmenukato' uya 'nokon iwenai pʉra rɨ man serɨ wakʉ ton pika'tɨto' pɨ'.
\v 2 Apʉne pʉra ipan pe epika'tɨpai ɨwe'to' kon i'tu uya, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨrɨ pɨ' Ma'sitoniya pon kon pɨ' utapurɨn pɨ' e'sa', to' auro'ka pɨ' nʉtɨtaine' wʉipiya si'kɨrɨ itʉrʉ pɨ' ɨmɨrɨ'nokon A'kaya pon kon ekonekasa' esi'pʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tu'kan kon tʉrʉnkasa' auya'nokon ɨnku'pai ɨwe'to' kon winɨ iku'nin pe, tukai'.
\v 3 E'tane pʉsamoro ina tonpa ton senno'ai' serɨ eseru yau ɨpɨ'nokon ina utapurɨto' esi namai' a'ta pe rɨ, e'tane tekonekai' ɨwesi kon pa, ta'pʉ uya na'ne' kasa.
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra ɨnʉ' rɨ Ma'sitoniya pon nɨ uye'sa' pe iyesi yau uya'kɨrɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyekonekasa' pe pʉra ɨyeporo kon pe iyesi a'tai, ina rɨ ɨpiyɨtʉ—ɨmɨrɨ'nokon kuru rɨ nɨrɨ ɨpiyɨtʉ—apʉne pʉra ina uya ayapurɨsa' kon pɨ'.
\v 5 Mɨrɨ pɨ' pʉsamoro utonpa ton enutɨ pɨ' usenuminka'pʉ to' uya aka'kʉranpato' kon pe, pena iwapiya parɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ekonekan nɨto' ton i'ma'kase'na amʉre'mʉra ɨntʉrʉnʉ kon ta'pʉ auya'nokon nʉ'pʉ tʉnin pe. Mɨrɨ a'tai, iyekonekasa' pe ɨwe'to' kon pe enpoikanin pe, ɨntʉrʉnʉ kon esi aya'kwarʉkasa' kon pe pʉra.
\s1 Amʉre'mʉra E'pɨn Nɨ
\p 
\v 6 Ɨyenu kon yau serɨ iku'tɨ': Ɨnʉ' rɨ mara ipɨnnin uya mara rɨ eporo, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨnʉ' rɨ amʉre'mʉra ipɨnnin uya amʉre'mʉra rɨ eporo.
\v 7 Tʉkaisarɨ'nokon to' nʉtʉrʉi tewan kon yau itʉto' pe tʉuya'nokon te'ku'sa' kon poro, ɨntʉpai pʉra esii'ma pen mɨrɨ pe pʉra e'kosonkosonmai'ma pen. Papa uya pori' pe esii'ma itʉnin i'nʉnka.
\v 8 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa uya wakʉ nonkasa' kupʉ mɨrɨ eke pe ɨpona'nokon, tu'kan yau rɨ tɨwɨrɨ rɨ, tanporon esa' pe i'se ɨwe'to' kon eke pe rɨ, tanporon wakʉ tʉrawaso yau eporo auya'nokon mɨrɨ.
\v 9 Iye'menukasa' na'ne' kasa:
\q1 “Tʉntʉrʉnʉ ta'nʉ'sa' iya mɨ poro rɨ entu'manin nan ena';
\q2 ipoken iko'manto' esi moro inke rɨ,”\f + \fr 9:9 \ft Eren 112:9\f*
\m tawon.
\v 10 Kʉrɨ ipɨnnin repanin itena'pɨ ke ite' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kiyari pe pʉreti ke, uya rɨ marɨ itʉrʉ mɨrɨpan uya eke pe ite' amʉranʉkʉ pa ikupʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipoken ɨwe'sa' rʉ'pʉ anʉmʉ kupʉ eke pe.\x - \xo 9:10 \xt Aisaya 55:10\x*
\v 11 Tanporon yau rɨ imaminke' pe ɨyena kon pa ɨku'to' kon oton, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ amʉre'mʉra te'repasen pe ɨwesi kon pa, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina awɨrɨ ɨye'repato' kon uya tenki tato' Papa pɨ' emapu'tɨto' pe.
\p 
\v 12 Serɨ epika'tɨn nɨto' mʉku'atʉi'ne' uya rɨken Papa munkɨ amʉ' repa pen e'tane eke pe iyanʉkʉ tenki tato' to' uya Papa pɨ' usenpoika.
\v 13 Apʉne pʉra tʉrawaso mʉku'atʉi'ne' uya ɨyenpoikasa' kon pɨ' ka'pon amʉ' uya Papa apurɨpɨ'to' oton main awɨrɨ ɨwe'to' kon uya Kʉrai ekareei ekamasa' uya itonpa'tɨsa' pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ amʉre'mʉra ɨye'repato' kon anta'nʉkʉnʉ kon to' ena' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon kon pokon pe rɨ.
\v 14 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' ɨpʉremato' ɨpona'nokon tewan kon yau utɨ ɨpiya'nokon, apʉne pʉra eke wakʉ nonkasa' Papa uya, uya ɨrepasa' kon pɨ'.
\v 15 Tenki kuru ta Papa pɨ', ekama entaino rɨ intʉrʉ'pʉ pɨ'!
\c 10
\s1 Paarʉ Uya Tʉtʉrawasooi Wapu'tɨ
\p 
\v 1 Eke pe pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mannʉ' pe Kʉrai e'to' winɨ uta'kwarʉka ɨpɨ'nokon—urɨ, Paarʉ, enari'kena' e'semʉ' pona e'sepon nɨsa' a'tai, e'tane enari'mʉn ɨnnɨ esi a'tai, tato' ipɨ'!
\v 2 Uye'sa' a'tai, ɨsɨ pe e'nin ɨpɨ'nokon e'to' kasa tʉron kon ka'pon amʉ' pɨ' serɨ non eseru yau uko'man nɨ tukai' tʉusenuminkasan.
\v 3 Non po rɨ ina uko'mantane, non nʉku'ai'ne' kasa ina usewa'noma esi pen.
\v 4 Ina epaai ton ina epanta'mato' ike ton esi non epanta'mato' ike kasa pʉra. Mɨrɨ kasa pʉra, Papa meruntɨrʉ esi to' piyau pana'pa' nan to' wapu ma'tanʉ'nin.
\v 5 E'sei'pɨ'nɨto' enkʉ'nʉkʉ ina uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon nɨ kasi Papa uya i'tuto' i'se pʉra te'sen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon nɨ usenuminkan nɨto' a'sisa' anʉmʉ ina uya Kʉrai maimu awɨron pe iye'to' pe.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyekonekasa' pe ina e'to' oton tanporon nɨ main awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨsa' kota'manin pe, tanporo ti'ma'kai' iyawɨrɨ ɨwe'sa' kon a'tai.
\p 
\v 7 Ipʉro'po rɨken ɨ'rɨ rɨ ene auya'nokon.\f + \fr 10:7 \fq Ipʉro'po rɨken ɨ'rɨ rɨ ena auya'nokon; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Ipʉro'po amʉ' pɨ' enpɨ'tɨ'.\f* Kʉrai iwano' pe ɨnʉ' rɨ e'kupʉ pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ nɨrɨ ni'tui ina esi Kʉrai iwano' pe, iyesi na'ne' kasa rɨ marɨ.
\v 8 Apʉne pʉra Itepuru meruntɨrʉ ina repa'pʉ iya ike esi ɨpika'tɨnin kon pe, ama'tanʉ'nin kon pe pen. Utapurɨ pe iyesi yau, mɨrɨ pɨ' ɨpiyɨtʉ pen.
\v 9 Ukaretaai ton ke ɨyenari'pa i'se 'nokon esi pe ɨsenpai pʉra e'ai'.
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra tʉron kon uya ta, “Ikaretaai ton esi sa'man mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pana' pe kuru, e'tane ka'pon pe iyesi yau ɨ'sɨ'mʉra rɨ iseta mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ isauro'to' esi notʉn nɨ,” ta.
\v 11 Kamoro rupɨ uya ito'ka'nʉkʉ e'pai iyesi karetaai wannɨ yau ta na'ne' esi mɨrɨ yau e'nɨ tane pʉra unku'ton kon pe iyesi mɨrɨ yau e'nɨ a'tai.
\p 
\v 12 Ina e'warinpa pen sa'ne mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉron kon tʉutapurɨsan eseru a'kɨrɨ teseru kon to'ka'nʉ'pɨtʉ pɨ' ina esi pen. Teseru kon i'tupɨtʉ to' uya teseru kon ke rɨ a'tai, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ teseru kon ke rɨ teseru kon aku'menka a'tai, ta'kwarʉ ke pʉra rɨ to' esi.
\v 13 Mɨrɨ pe rɨ iye'tane, wakʉ pe iye'to' entai rɨ ina utapurɨ pen, e'tane ina utapurɨto' kupʉ ina uya Papa uya ina ku'sa' na'ne' awɨrɨ iteseru, ɨyepoton kon nɨ.
\v 14 Siya kuru rɨ mɨ pe te'ku'to' kon yau ina utɨ pen, ɨpiya'nokon ina uye'sa' pʉra iyesi yau, mɨrɨ kasa nin si nesii'no apʉne pʉra si Kʉrai ekareei esa' pe rɨ ina uye'kaa'pʉ ɨpiya'nokon.
\v 15 Tʉpʉ'kʉ kon entai siya kuru nɨrɨ ina utɨ pen tʉron kon nʉkupʉ'pʉ tʉrawaso pɨ' tʉutapurɨ kon winɨ. Ina e'ku'to' esi mɨrɨ,\f + \fr 10:15 \ft Mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fv 13 \fq E'tane rɨ, ina utapurɨ pen nɨ i'tu pokena' pen nɨ pɨ', e'tane ina utapurɨ Papa uya i'tuto' ike ke ina uya iku'to' pe iku'sa' na'ne' ke—i'tuto' ike ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ ku'to' ike. \fv 14 \fq … \fv 15 \fq Ina utapurɨ pʉra iyesi i'tu pokena' pen nɨ pɨ' tʉron kon nɨ tʉrawasooi rʉ'pʉ pɨ'\f* miyarɨ rɨ apurɨto' auya'nokon usemo'ka koro'tau, ɨ'koro'tau'nokon ina nʉkupʉnʉ e'waraukato' oton eke pe kuru,
\v 16 ina uya itekare ekamato' pe itekare ke a'pɨ'sa' pen pata ton nono yau'ne ɨyentau'nokon, apʉne pʉra ka'pon uya rɨ itekare ekama'pʉ yau itekare tekamai' atapurɨpai pʉra ina esi pɨ'.
\v 17 E'tane, “Tɨwɨ atapurɨpaino nʉtapurɨi Itepuru yau,”\f + \fr 10:17 \ft Iseremaya 9:24\f* tasa'.
\v 18 Apʉne pʉra ka'pon tiwano' pe tʉutapurɨsen pɨ' wakʉ ta pʉra iyesi e'tane ka'pon Itepuru napurɨnʉ pɨ' rɨken.
\c 11
\s1 Paarʉ Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Ennakanin Nan Enno'sa' Kon
\p 
\v 1 Mara rʉ'kwɨ iya'kwarʉ pʉra e'ai'ne' yau a'kʉre'tɨ auya'nokon tukai' e'ku'ai', e'tane iku'kapʉ auya'nokon nɨ.
\v 2 Papa uya tasa' kasa ɨkɨntato' yau ɨkɨntayai' ɨpɨ'nokon. Tikin nan ataan'pʉ ena' ɨtʉto' pe uya usauro'sa', Kʉrai ena', a'pɨ'pʉn kuru uri'san pe ɨtʉto' pe uya itena'.
\v 3 E'tane enari'ke' e'ai' ɨkʉi uya I' enku'tɨ'pʉ kasa enku'tɨn nɨto' ike ke ɨusenuminkato' kon utano'ma, i'nai rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ esuken ɨye'tʉsa' kon Kʉrai ena' apai.\x - \xo 11:3 \xt Iseneses 3:1-5, 13\x*
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra ɨnʉ' rɨ uyepʉ pe iyesi yau ɨpiya'nokon Sises ekareei ekamase'na, Sises ekareei ina nekama'pʉ warai pen nɨ, mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉponaron nɨ a'kwarʉ anʉnsa' auya'nokon yau, ananʉmʉ'pʉ kon warai pen, mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉponaron nɨ wakʉ itekare ana'si'pʉ kon warai pen, inke pʉra rɨ iya' ɨyena kon.
\v 5 E'tane usenuminka pʉra iyesi aiko pe esi eke ton enno'sa' kon o'koi' tukai'.
\v 6 Wakʉ pe kuru anpisin koro'tau tʉusauro'sen pe isenupasa' pen urɨ, e'tane i'tunin pe rɨ esi. Serɨ ton ku'sa' ina uya man wakʉ pe kuru ene poken nɨ tanporon winɨ rɨ.
\p 
\v 7 Makoi pe pe' iyesi'pʉ u'tɨto' ayanʉnnin kon pe Papa ekareei ekama uya winɨ te'masen pe pʉra?
\v 8 Tʉron nɨ ton so'si amʉ' rapumasa' uya to' e'repato' mo'ka uya winɨ ɨpika'tɨnin kon pe.
\v 9 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpiyau'nokon esi a'tai, ɨ'rɨ rʉ'kwɨ rɨ i'se esi pɨ', ɨnʉ' rɨ tewankamai' esi'pʉ pen, apʉne pʉra Ma'sitoniya winɨ iye'sa' kon utonpa ton uya i'se e'to' ke urepa'pʉ. Ɨ'rɨ winɨ rɨ ɨyewankamanin kon pe pʉra enkurumʉ'pʉ, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ esi miyarɨ rɨ.\x - \xo 11:9 \xt Piri'pai 4:15-18\x*
\v 10 I'nai rɨ, i'nairon Kʉrai eseru esi pɨ' uyau, ɨnʉ' rɨ A'kaya nono ton awon uya serɨ utapurɨto' ereutanʉkʉ pʉra rɨ iyesi.
\v 11 Ɨ'rɨ pe iyesi pɨ'? Apʉne pʉra ɨi'nʉnka uya 'nokon pʉra iyesi pɨ' pe'? Ɨi'nʉnka uya 'nokon i'tu Papa uya!
\v 12 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ rɨ siku'ai'ne' kupʉ pɨ' esi non akʉ'to' pe uya kamoro tʉweyu kon eporo i'se te'san o'noro ukaisarɨ'nokon e'paino kon tʉutapurɨto' kon yau.
\p 
\v 13 Kamoro waraino kon esi mɨrɨ ennakanin nan enno'sa' kon pe, usenku'tɨn nɨto' tʉrawasomanin nan, Kʉrai nennoko'san pe te'ku'san.
\v 14 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usenuminkan pe pʉra, Se'tan\f + \fr 11:14 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* nɨ e'kupʉ a'kwa inserʉʉi pe.
\v 15 Mɨrɨ wenai, usewansiukan pe pʉra, ipoitorʉ ton e'kupʉ pe iyesi a'tai ipokena' pe e'nɨto' poitorʉ pe. To' weyu u'ma'to' oton to' nʉkupʉnʉ nʉwarinpanʉ pe.
\s1 Tekota'ma Pɨ' Paarʉ Utapurɨto'
\p 
\v 16 Akonoma uya: Iya'kwarʉ pʉn pe rɨ ɨnʉ' rɨ uku'nin, e'tane ikupʉ auya'nokon yau, uyanʉntɨ' si iya'kwarʉ pʉn kupʉ pe, mara rʉ'kwɨ utapurɨn nɨto' ku'to' pe uya.
\v 17 Serɨ iwano' wannɨ pe en yau e'ku'nɨto', Itepuru kasa usaurokʉ pen nɨ, e'tane iya'kwarʉ pʉn kasa.
\v 18 Tu'kan kon nɨ utapurɨ pɨ' non nʉkupʉnʉ kasa, urɨ nɨrɨ utapurɨ.
\v 19 Pori' pe iya'kwarʉ pʉnon kon pɨ' ɨwesi kon, ta'kwarʉ ke ɨwesi kon pɨ' kuru si!
\v 20 I'nai rɨ kuru, to' uya aya'sisa' kon tapiyo' kon pe, mɨrɨ pe pʉra aiko pe rɨ to' uya ɨku'sa' kon, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨpɨ'nokon nɨ to' usennakasa', mɨrɨ pe pʉra awapiya'nokon nɨ iye'sara'tɨpɨ'sa' pe to' esi, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ɨyemʉ' kon pɨ' to' uya ɨwɨpɨ'sa' kon.
\v 21 Epiyɨ'to' yau, a'tu'mʉra kuru ina esi ukayai' mɨrɨ kasa e'nɨsa' pɨ'!
\p Ɨ'rɨ pɨ' rɨken ɨnʉ' rɨ atapurɨpai nai—usaurokʉ iya'kwarʉ pʉn kasa—urɨ kuru rɨ utapurɨ mɨrɨ pɨ'.
\v 22 Ipuru amʉ' pe pe' to' esi? Urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ esi. Esuwerʉ amʉ' pe pe' to' esi? Urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ esi. Epʉra'an payan nʉ'san pe pe' to' esi? Urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ esi.
\v 23 Kʉrai poitorʉ pe pe' to' esi? Usenuminkato' yau pʉra rɨ na'kɨ e'ai' serɨ kasa usauro'to' pe, to' entaino rɨ urɨ. Sa'man pe kuru e'tʉrawasoma'pʉ, pariki'si tau ɨsipɨkɨrɨ'ne kuru, ɨsɨ pe kuru ari'po'pɨ'sa' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inke ite'kwa'ne rɨ eri'nɨto' ya' a'ko pe utɨpɨ'sa'.\x - \xo 11:23 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:23\x*
\v 24 5 kaisa rɨ ite'kwa Esuwerʉ amʉ' winɨ 40 kaisa rɨ tikin nɨ iyapai tʉmo'kai' utari'po'pɨ'nɨto' eporo'pʉ uya.\x - \xo 11:24 \xt Isu'taronomi 25:3\x*
\v 25 Osorʉwau ite'kwa uyari'po'pɨtʉ'pʉ yʉi ke, tikin ite'kwa tɨ' ke uwɨpɨtʉ'pʉ, osorʉwau ite'kwa uyen pe iye'tane kanau epotorʉ'pʉ uta'morʉpɨtʉ'pʉ, tikin nɨ ewarupɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tikin nɨ wʉi ennoko'pʉ uya parau kau,\x - \xo 11:25 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:22; 14:19\x*
\v 26 utɨn pɨ' rɨ uko'manpɨ'tai. Ɨsɨ yau rɨ esi'pʉ tuna kau, ɨsɨ yau ama' e' ton koro'tau, ɨsɨ yau uwaraino kon Esuwerʉ amʉ' koro'tau rɨ, ɨsɨ yau Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen koro'tau; ɨsɨ yau eke pata yau rɨ, ɨsɨ yau eke pata pʉ'kʉ yau, ɨsɨ yau parau po; mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsɨ yau ennakanin nan utonpa ton pe te'ku'se koro'tau.\x - \xo 11:26 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 9:23; 14:15\x*
\v 27 E'tʉrawasomasa' man, e'tʉrawasomasa' man sa'man pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inke ite'kwa e'nʉmʉ pʉra; iwan pe e'nɨto' i'tusa' uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tuna'kiri' ke mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kiyari pʉra e'pɨ'sa'; ikomi' pe e'pɨ'sa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipon pʉra.
\v 28 Tanporon piyapai, wʉi kaisa rɨ usewankaman pɨ' esi'pʉ so'si amʉ' pɨ'.
\v 29 Ɨnʉ' esi ɨ'sɨ'mʉra, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ si ɨ'sɨ'mʉra usi'tu pʉra? Ɨnʉ' arɨ'pʉ makoi ya', u'nau epo'tɨ pʉra ipɨkɨrɨ?
\p 
\v 30 Utapurɨ pe iyesi yau, utapurɨ rɨ ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'to' enpoikanin pɨ'.
\v 31 Papa, Itepuru Sises e'to' itese' pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Ikʉipʉnʉ, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ tapurɨpɨ'sen pe te'sen uya i'tu, kasi pe pʉra esi.
\v 32 Tamaskas yau kopʉna, kin Are'tas o'noron uya pata Tamaskas erasuntɨ'pʉ, urɨ a'sito' pe.
\v 33 E'tane pa'siki'ti yau unu'tɨ'pʉ, iwekupiri wintooi awɨrɨ, mɨrɨpan enapai emo'ka'pʉ.\x - \xo 11:33 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 9:23-25\x*
\c 12
\s1 Paarʉ Enu Uta'kwakasa' Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Itikʉ
\p 
\v 1 Utapurɨn pɨ' rɨ esii'ya. Wakʉ epoton pʉra rɨ iye'tane, en uta'kwakato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ isenpoikato' pɨ' Itepuru winɨ pɨ' rɨ esii'ya.
\v 2 Ka'pon si'tuyai' Kʉrai yawon, 14 kaisa rɨ wʉipiya utɨkaa'pʉ serɨ itosorʉwano Epʉn pona iyenuku'pʉ awonsi'kɨ. Tʉpun tau rɨ nawon mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉpun tau pʉra rɨ nawon i'tu uya pʉra rɨ iyesi—Papa uya i'tu.
\v 3 I'tu uya si, pʉse rɨ ka'pon—tʉpun tau mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉpun tapai rɨ nawon i'tu uya pʉra rɨ iyesi, e'tane Papa uya i'tu —
\v 4 utanʉmʉ'pʉ wakʉ pe Papa pata'se' ya'. Ekama pokena' pen nɨ eta'pʉ iya, ka'pon uya ekamato' pe tato' pen nɨ.
\v 5 Kʉrɨ rɨ waraino ka'pon pɨ' utapurɨ, e'tane upɨ' utapurɨ pen, ɨ'sɨ'mʉra rɨken e'to' pɨ' utapurɨ.
\v 6 Utapurɨ pe iyesi yau, iya'kwarʉ pʉn pe esi pen, apʉne pʉra i'nairon pɨ' usaurokʉ pe iyesi. E'tane ikupʉ uya pen, eke pe rɨ urɨ tʉku'se ɨnʉ' rɨ usenuminka namai' upɨ' unkuu'pʉ pɨ' mɨrɨ pe pʉra ta'pʉ uya pɨ' tesi entai.
\p 
\v 7 Utaperʉkan pɨ' esi namai', serɨ ton eke pe rɨ isenpoikasa' rʉ'pʉ uyena' pɨ', itikʉ e'tʉrʉ'pʉ upun ya', Se'tan\f + \fr 12:7 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* maimu ne'nin pe, ipan pe rɨ ukota'manin pe.
\v 8 Osorʉwau ite'kwa ipan pe Itepuru ekama'po'pʉ uya upiyapai imo'kato' pe iya.
\v 9 E'tane, “Urɨ uya wakʉ nonkasa' esi eke pe ɨiwano' pe, apʉne pʉra umeruntɨrʉ ekoneka wakʉ pe ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'nɨto' yau,” ta'pʉ iya upɨ'. Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', utapurɨ miyarɨ parɨ pori' pe esii'ma ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'to' pɨ', Kʉrai meruntɨrʉ ereutato' pe upona.
\v 10 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', Kʉrai uriya', urɨ esi pori' pe ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'nɨto' yau, sapeman nɨto' yau, sa'man pe e'nɨto' yau, wakʉ kupʉ wenai kota'man nɨto' yau, sa'man ikupʉ pokena' pen yau. Apʉne pʉra ɨ'sɨ'mʉra esi a'tai, mɨrɨ a'tai pana' pe rɨ esi.
\s1 Paarʉ Usewankamato' Koren Pon Kon Pɨ'
\p 
\v 11 Uiwano' pe rɨ iya'kwarʉ pʉra enasa' serɨ, e'tane sa'ne ɨmɨrɨ'nokon uya iku'to' pe uya ikuu'pʉ. Uyekama pe masauro'tʉi'no e'tane, apʉne pʉra aiko pe esi pen eke ton itekare ekamai' enno'sa' kon o'koi', ɨnʉ' pe pʉra rɨ sa'ne e'tane.
\v 12 Mɨ ton itekare ekamai' enno'sa' ma'kʉi'tɨnin—ento' ipɨ' ton, usenuminkan nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke Papa tʉrawasooi—e'kuu'pʉ ɨ'koro'tau'nokon eke rɨ sa'man annawɨrɨ.
\v 13 Nai kasa ken tʉron nɨ ton so'si amʉ' o'koi' aiko pe ɨwesi'pʉ kon, ɨpɨ'nokon nɨken upika'tɨtɨ' tasa' uya pʉra iyesi pɨ' pe'? Ipokena' pen unkuu'pʉ pɨ' si upɨ' ɨsentu'matɨ'!
\p 
\v 14 Serɨ si e'kama utɨn pɨ' aka'kʉranpai'nokon itosorʉwano ite'kwa pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ upika'tɨtɨ' ta uya pen ɨpɨ'nokon, apʉne pʉra ɨimamin kon i'se esi pen e'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon. Apʉne pʉra mʉre amʉ' esi tʉsanon kon potawa'tɨnin nan pe pen, e'tane to' sanon uya nin to' potawa'tɨ.
\v 15 Mɨrɨ kasa si ɨpɨ'nokon pori' pe esii'ma tanporon nɨ uyenawon ennoko uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ rɨ nɨrɨ si. Ipan pe pe' ɨi'nʉnka uya 'nokon yau, mara rʉ'kwɨ pe' ui'nʉnka auya'nokon?
\v 16 Iyesi'pʉ na'ne' kasa si iyesi yau, upika'tɨ auya'nokon i'se pʉra esi'pʉ. Mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane ennakanin pe esi'pʉ enku'tɨn nɨto' winɨ ɨyeparantɨ'pʉ uya 'nokon ta!
\v 17 Kɨnyennakata'tʉi pe' ɨpʉrataai kon mo'kato' pe uya ka'pon amʉ' unennoko'san winɨ?
\v 18 Tai'tas apiyo'ma'pʉ uya ipan pe ɨpiya'nokon itɨto' pe, mɨrɨpan a'kɨrɨ utonpa kon ennoko'pʉ uya. Tai'tas uya ken pe' ɨyennaka'pʉ kon ɨpʉrataai kon mo'kato' pe tʉuya? Ɨsi'kaisaron kon pen pe' ina ta'kwarʉ kon yau tʉnkupʉnʉ kon yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsiporon nɨ pen pe' ina eseru?
\p 
\v 19 Usenuminkan pɨ' pe' ɨwesi'pʉ kon mɨsi'kɨrɨ rɨ ɨpɨ'nokon ina e'wapu'tɨ tukai'? Usauro'nɨ pɨ' sa'ne ina e'sa' serɨ ko Papa uya tentane'nokon Kʉrai yawon kon pe; utonpa ton nʉ'kwɨ, tanporon ina nʉku'ai'ne' esi ɨmeruntɨtanʉ'nin kon pe.
\v 20 Enari'nʉnyai' ɨpiya'nokon utɨsa' a'tai, ɨyeporo uya 'nokon poken pʉra rɨ iyesi i'se e'to' awɨrɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ nɨrɨ i'se ɨwe'to' kon awɨrɨ pʉra. Enari'nʉnyai' ɨsipɨ' rɨ te'san, tɨkɨntasan nɨ, tʉusakorotasan nɨ, tʉpoirɨ'nokon nɨ te'san nɨ, kasi pe ka'pon eseru'tɨnin nan nɨ, ɨri ka'pon eseru pɨ' tʉusauro'san nɨ, i'tunin pe rɨ tesi kon pɨ' mɨ pa'nan nɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itanpokʉmasa' pe rɨ ɨyeporo uya 'nokon poken iyesi.
\v 21 Enari'nʉnyai' utɨka'sa' a'tai kanan Papa itese' pɨ' e'to' uya se pe rɨ uku'to' oton arau'nokon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipan pe rɨ upokoitato' oton tu'kan kon imakoitasa' kon pena iwa wenai iyera'tɨsa' pʉra na'ne' nan ɨri apai, tekumato' kon apai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri i'se te'to' kon ku'to' tʉuya'nokon apai, ikupʉ pɨ' tesi'pʉ kon.
\c 13
\s1 Iu'matʉ Pe Panaman Nɨto'
\p 
\v 1 Serɨ si itosorʉwano ite'kwa pe aka'kʉranpai'nokon utɨ. “Moro ɨ'rɨ e'ku'sa' rʉ'pʉ esi pɨ' asa'ron kon mɨrɨ pe pʉra osorʉwawon kon usauro'to' pe iyesi,”\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Isu'taronomi 19:15\f* tasa'.
\v 2 Apanamakaa'pʉ uya 'nokon ɨpiyau'nokon esi a'tai iyakon ite'kwa pe. Akonoma uya ɨpiyau'nokon pʉra esii'ma: Enna'posa' a'tai, ɨnʉ' rɨ e'wanpa uya pen kamoro pena iwa imakoitasa' kon pe na'ne' nan mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉron kon nɨ,
\v 3 ipan pe ɨni'tupai ɨwesi kon pɨ' Kʉrai usauro'to' uporo. Ɨ'sɨ'mʉn pen kʉrɨ rɨ ɨmɨrɨ'nokon koneka pɨ' tesi yau, e'tane meruntɨ pe iyesi ɨ'koro'tau'nokon.
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra i'nai rɨ iye'to' pe, kurusu' pona ipokapɨtʉ'pʉ ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yau, e'tane si iko'mamʉ Papa meruntɨrʉ winɨ. Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ, iyau ɨ'sɨ'mʉra e'nɨ'nokon, e'tane si Papa meruntɨrʉ winɨ ina uko'mamʉ ipokon pe ayapiyo' kon pe.
\p 
\v 5 Ɨsentɨ' apurɨto' yau rɨ pe' ɨwesi kon tukai'; ɨsi'tutɨ' ɨiwano' kon pe. I'tu auya'nokon pʉra pe' iyesi Kʉrai esi ayau'nokon?—ɨusi'tuto' kon yau rɨ nin auta'mo'kasa' kon a'tai rɨken i'tu auya'nokon ipʉra iyesi?
\v 6 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sapurɨyai' ito'ka'nʉkʉ auya'nokon usi'tun nɨto' yau uta'mo'kan nɨsa' pʉra iyesi.
\v 7 Serɨ si ina ɨpʉrema Papa pɨ' ipokena' pen kupʉ auya'nokon namai'. Ka'pon amʉ' uya en nɨto' pe pen nɨ usi'tun nɨto' yau entakasa', e'tane ipokena' pe te'sen kupʉ kon pa ita'mo'kasa' pe rɨ e'ku'nɨ tane.
\v 8 Apʉne pʉra ɨ'rɨ rɨ kupʉ poken pʉra ina uya iyesi i'nairon ewa'noma pe, e'tane i'nairon iwano' pe rɨken.
\v 9 Ina epori'ma ɨ'sɨ'mʉra tesi kon a'tai e'tane pana' pe ɨwesi kon; ina ɨpʉremato' nin si esi mɨrɨ wakʉ pe ɨwesi kon pa.
\v 10 Mɨrɨ wenai serɨ ton menuka uya serɨ ɨpiyau'nokon pʉra esii'ma, utɨsa' a'tai ɨsɨ pe umeruntɨrʉ apurɨ uya namai'—umeruntɨrʉ Itepuru uya urepa'pʉ ike ke ɨkonekanin kon pe, ama'tanʉ'nin kon pe pen.
\s1 Iu'matʉ Pe Miyarɨ Tato'
\p 
\v 11 Iu'matʉ pe, utonpa ton, ɨisirɨ'nokon. Wakʉ pe e'nɨto' pɨ' ɨse'se'tɨtɨ', ipan pe ɨyekama'poto' uya 'nokon etatɨ', tikin nɨ isenuminkato' e'tɨ', tʉusewa'nomai' pʉra ɨko'mantɨ'. Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa usi'nʉnkan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨ ku'nin esi mɨrɨ ɨpiyau'nokon.
\p 
\v 12 Miyarɨ ta auya'nokon e'kwa pe ɨtonpa kon pɨ' wakʉ eseru yau ata'su'katɨ'.
\v 13 Tanporo wakʉ ton man miyarɨ ta pɨ' ɨpɨ'nokon.
\p 
\v 14 Tɨwɨ eke rɨ wakʉ Itepuru Sises Kʉrai nʉnonka'pʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa usi'nʉnkato', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Wakʉ A'kwarʉ amʉtʉ pe e'nɨto' nesii tanporo ɨpiyau'nokon.
